          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若败下阵来，怎么样说？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愿将六阳魁首悬挂营门！俺若得胜回来呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁术",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我将催粮印信付汝掌管！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "口说无凭，必要立下军令状。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张翼德三击掌打赌争斗，\n表家乡范阳镇在那涿州。\n结桃园拜金兰同把军投。\n倘若是败阵回悬挂人头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕布儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三爹爹擒了你才把功收。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁术",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人败阵必逃走，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军有勇必有谋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈哈。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹操、袁术同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "袁术→张飞",
          "turns": 4
        },
        {
          "edge": "张飞→袁术",
