    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "吕布",
        "四上手",
        "四将官",
        "四白文堂"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四白文堂、四上手、四将官、纛旗引吕布同上，吕布起霸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少小英雄镇虎牢，狐群鼠辈怎脱逃？咚咚画鼓催军进，指日奏凯旋还朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，温侯吕布。只因前部先锋华雄，被关云长斩于阵前，相父大怒，命俺统领\n精兵十万，挡住虎牢关。相父大兵随后接应，共灭烽烟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "推开龙马勒锦辔，试看一战表凌烟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，兵发虎牢关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四白文堂、四上手、四将官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "吕布→四将官",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "念": 1,
          "同白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "关羽",
        "刘备"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起初更鼓〗。二小军掌灯引刘备同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金兰人暗地悄探，\n满天星斗夜生寒。\n一声孤雁好伤惨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，刘备。剿灭黄巾有功，特授平原县令。朝中董卓弄权，同公孙将军前来讨\n贼。苍天哪苍天，可念大汉祀统，早灭烽烟，万民乐业，某之愿也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉华夷渐倾颓使人感叹，\n怎能够诛叛臣国泰民安。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起二更鼓〗。关羽上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听大哥在月下长吁短叹，\n多因是恨董卓搅乱江山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥为何在此长叹？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二弟你还不知，只因三弟与袁术立下军状，要生擒吕布。倘若败阵如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且待天明，你我弟兄二人助三弟一膀之力。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二弟言之有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "异姓同胞共患难，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惟愿得胜建功还。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、关羽同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "刘备→关羽",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "关羽→刘备",
          "turns": 2
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 7,
          "唱": 3,
          "白": 3
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.5,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "关羽",
        "刘备",
        "吕布",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人情势利古今残，谁识英雄实非凡？安得快人如翼德，尽诛世上负心男。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可笑袁术，与俺打赌生擒吕布。啊，老张的丈八蛇矛，在那里瞪眉瞪眼，待俺\n将它磨洗磨洗。枪吓枪，你明日见了吕布，将他一枪挑下马来，咱老子就封你\n一个枪将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖上半段风入松〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，看天色尚早，待俺老张打睡片时。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起三更鼓〗。关羽、刘备同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令严鼓角三更尽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夜宿貔貅百万兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是后营，听他说些什么。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起四更鼓〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊哈哈哈，天哪天，你怎的不明？鸡吓吓鸡，你怎的不叫？想是吕布死时未到，\n待俺老张再打个盹儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听三弟之言，战心大胜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待弟将他唤醒，天明一同出马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且待他歇息片时，明日好与吕布交战。我等相随助他成功便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理。请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、关羽同下。〖起五更鼓〗。鸡叫。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈，好了。听樵楼五更鸡叫，天已明，吕布小儿死期到了。老张就此杀上\n前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监、四文堂自两边分上。〖下半段风入松〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，吕布小儿出关受死！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四白文堂、吕布同上，开城。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，来者黑汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕布小儿着鞭！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布、张飞同杀，吕布败下，张飞追下，吕布上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，方才关前来一黑汉，十分猛勇，待他追来，使花枪伤他便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，吕布哪里走？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞败下，吕布追下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "张飞→刘备",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "刘备→关羽",
          "turns": 4
