      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "关羽",
        "刘备",
        "吕布",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、关羽同上，两边望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二弟，三弟大战吕布，惟恐有失，你催马助战便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。张飞急上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还是四弟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桃园。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还是杏园！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你与吕布交战，胜败如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺也不知谁胜谁败。俺在前面走，他在后面追。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢是败了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，败了，败了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你与袁术打赌一事，怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，大哥、二哥，看在桃园结义分上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢，你我三人，一马上，三马上；一马下，三马下。扣定连环，大战吕布便\n了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好哇，随兄弟杀上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟，到了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吓，到了虎牢关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急三枪〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到了关前，大哥、二哥前去叫关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟叫关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔呔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟高声叫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥、二哥，吕布那个囚囊的勇不可挡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不妨，有我二人在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是吓，有大哥、二哥在此。\n呔，吕布出关受死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开关！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布上，打过场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁，原来是你。你这败将又来则甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你管老子败不败。再来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、关羽、张飞同打过场，刘备、张飞同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来将通名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷关云长。看刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布、关羽同过合，对杀，刘备上，接杀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来将通名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘玄德。看剑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布、刘备对杀，张飞上，接杀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀了半日，不曾问你这黑贼名姓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈。吕布小儿听着：老子姓张名飞字翼德，涿州范阳人也。自破黄巾以来，\n诸侯闻名丧胆。手执丈八蛇矛，吕布小儿你怕是不怕？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张翼德威名人皆晓，\n我今擒你献功劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、关羽、张飞同杀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕布，你敢是怯战？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是老爷怯战。黑贼可认得你吕老爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺认得你是四姓的家奴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他只有三姓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥、二哥哪里知道。他本姓吕，投了丁建阳。杀了丁建阳，投了董卓。咱弟\n兄们灭了董卓，投入桃园，岂不是四姓的家奴？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好匹夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一言怒满三千丈，\n胆大匹夫把我伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "泗水关斩了华雄将，\n无名小辈逞刚强。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "董卓残暴把君抗，\n重整汉室诛贼亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四姓家奴名节丧，\n留得臭名万载扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕布",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "出兵会过多少将，\n三马连环不见强。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕布败下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽、张飞、刘备",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎穴龙潭战一场！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽、张飞、刘备同追下。）"
        }
      ],
